{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Operations/Sqrt.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.sqrt\"><span class=\"name\">Float</span>.<span class=\"name\">Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnpackedFloat</span>.<span class=\"name\">sqrt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">spec</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.html#Float.Model.Format\">Format</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Basic.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat\">UnpackedFloat</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Basic.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat\">UnpackedFloat</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Computes the square root of a floating-point number and rounds the result according to the given\nspecification.\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Operations/Sqrt.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.sqrt","kind":"def","line":39,"name":"Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.sqrt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Operations/Sqrt.lean#L39-L51"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Operations/Sqrt.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.sqrtCore\"><span class=\"name\">Float</span>.<span class=\"name\">Model</span>.<span class=\"name\">UnpackedFloat</span>.<span class=\"name\">sqrtCore</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">spec</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Format/Basic.html#Float.Model.Format\">Format</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int\">Int</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Init/Data/Int/Basic.html#Int\">Int</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Round.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.Accuracy\">Accuracy</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Computes a `(mantissa, exponent)` pair for the square root with enough bits to populate the mantissa\nfor the given specification. Also returns an `Accuracy` stating how the returned pair relates to\nthe infinitely precise square root.\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Operations/Sqrt.html#Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.sqrtCore","kind":"def","line":18,"name":"Float.Model.UnpackedFloat.sqrtCore","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/Float/Model/Unpacked/Operations/Sqrt.lean#L18-L37"}}],"imports":["Init.Data.Float.Model.Unpacked.Round","Init.Data.Nat.Sqrt.Basic"],"instances":[],"name":"Init.Data.Float.Model.Unpacked.Operations.Sqrt"}